---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Navbar from "../../components/Navbar.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="p-2">
    <div class="flex justify-center flex-col mt-5 gap-5 items-center">
      <Image
        transition:persist
        class="rounded-full scale-ani shadow-lg"
        width={300}
        height={300}
        alt={"profile"}
        src={"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ogw/AGvuzYYdATWLe1mE5MSEgs3KlUXC7j8-ig63Y_0gw8y3zNM=s300-c-mo"}
      />
      <h3 class="font-bold text-4xl">Kalaiarasan Senthil</h3>
    </div>
    <section class="max-w-7xl mt-10 mx-auto text-justify">
      Someone who is <span class="bg-primary px-2 text-white"
        >constantly learning</span
      >
       new things and interested in making apps which make a better living. I
      have been always amazed by the <span class="bg-primary px-2 text-white">
        technology
      </span>
       around me and the potential it has. Truely it makes our <span
        class="bg-primary px-2 text-white">lives</span
      > better. Being a tech enthusiast, I am using apps that foresees the
      future to be always better than present. In the journey of life, I am very
      much <span class="bg-primary px-2 text-white">kind</span> and blessed to
      make apps that change the <span class="bg-primary px-2 text-white"
        >world.</span
      >
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
